#: ../../P/programming.rst:5
msgid "programming"
msgstr "programming"

#: ../../P/programming.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../P/programming.rst:10
msgid ""
"The art of debugging a blank sheet of paper (or, in these days of on-line "
"editing, the art of debugging an empty file). \"Bloody instructions which, "
"being taught, return to plague their inventor\" (*Macbeth*\\, Act 1, Scene "
"7)"
msgstr ""
"白紙の紙(あるいは、オンライン編集の今日では、空のファイル)をデバッグする芸術。「教えられると、考案者を悩ますために戻ってくる血なまぐさい指示」(\\ "
"*Macbeth*\\ 、第1幕第7場)"

#: ../../P/programming.rst:14
msgid ""
"A pastime similar to banging one's head against a wall, but with fewer "
"opportunities for reward."
msgstr "壁に頭をぶつけるのに似た娯楽だが、報酬の機会はより少ない。"

#: ../../P/programming.rst:17
msgid "The most fun you can have with your clothes on."
msgstr "服を着たままでできる最も楽しいこと。"

#: ../../P/programming.rst:20
msgid "The least fun you can have with your clothes off."
msgstr "服を脱いでできる最もつまらないこと。"
